Lane polylogue-daemon-forensics, worktree = your cwd, branch feature/fanout/daemon-forensics.
MISSION: polylogue-peo — daemon death leaves no trace: crash forensics + heartbeat sentinel + restart policy. OWN: daemon lifecycle/startup paths + ops-tier event writes + tests. AVOID: web_shell (another lane), convergence usage-refresh (another lane).
